IKEv1 SITE TO SITE POLICY BASED VPN LAB

Topology

PC1 —- R1 —- ISP —- R2 —- PC2

LAN Networks 192.168.63.0/24 192.168.64.0/24

WAN Links R1 - ISP : 10.63.1.0/30 R2 - ISP : 10.63.2.0/30

======================== ROUTER R1 CONFIGURATION
========================

hostname R1

interface e0/1 no switchport ip address 10.63.1.1 255.255.255.252 no
shutdown

interface e0/2 no switchport ip address 192.168.63.1 255.255.255.0 no
shutdown

ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.63.1.2 ip route 192.168.64.0 255.255.255.0
10.63.1.2

crypto isakmp policy 10 encryption aes hash sha authentication pre-share
group 2 lifetime 86400

crypto isakmp key cisco address 10.63.2.2

crypto ipsec transform-set TS esp-aes esp-sha-hmac

ip access-list extended VPN-TRAFFIC permit ip 192.168.63.0 0.0.0.255
192.168.64.0 0.0.0.255

crypto map CMAP 10 ipsec-isakmp set peer 10.63.2.2 set transform-set TS
match address VPN-TRAFFIC

interface e0/1 crypto map CMAP

